# 🌿 Lepax

> **Plan less, lepak more.**

A social hangout app for Malaysians — built to turn casual "anyone free?" into actual plans without the usual group chat chaos.

---

## The problem

You've been there. Someone drops "jom" in the group chat. Five people react. Nobody decides where. The thread dies. Plans fizzle before they start.

Lepax fixes the coordination gap between *wanting to hang out* and *actually hanging out*. Post a plan, see what friends are doing, join or fork someone else's itinerary. No algorithm. No noise. Just plans.

