| Database | Cloud Firestore |
| Image uploads | Cloudinary (free tier, no billing) |
| Navigation | React Navigation v7 |
| State | React Context + hooks |

---

## Features

**Plans as social objects**
- Create plans with visibility: private, friends-only, or public
- 4-step creation flow: visibility → when & where → itinerary → vibe tags

**Fork the lepak** *(the gimmick)*
- Every public plan shows a fork count
- Fork any plan to copy its full itinerary to your own draft
- Credit is given to the original host — good planners get recognition

**Friend feed**
- Chronological, no algorithm
- See what friends are planning, join with one tap

**Explore**
- Discover public plans by geo radius: 5km / 20km / 50km / anywhere
- Filter by vibe: chill, foodie, adventure, budget, spontaneous

**"Also free?" nudges**
- See which friends have no plans today
- Send a quick "jom mamak?" nudge or broadcast to everyone at once

**Profiles**
- Avatar upload via Cloudinary
- Stats: plans hosted, forks received, friend count
- Bio editing

---

## What's intentionally NOT in this app

| Skipped | Why |
|---|---|
| In-app chat | Use WhatsApp or Telegram — no point competing |
| Payments | Touch n Go and DuitNow exist |
| Reviews / ratings | Too transactional, kills the vibe |
| Algorithmic feed | Chronological is honest |
| Stories / shorts | Noise, not signal |

